WEBVTT

00:00:00.663 --> 00:00:03.958
My life is reflected in my tattoos,

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.837
and you're going to have to trust me
when I say that I've got a lot of them.

00:00:07.879 --> 00:00:09.630
My body art tells a story.

00:00:09.672 --> 00:00:12.884
Now, my HIV tattoo
is on one of my kneecaps,

00:00:12.925 --> 00:00:14.844
which is the joint that,

00:00:14.844 --> 00:00:17.055
through a career of playing
professional rugby,

00:00:17.096 --> 00:00:18.264
was shot to pieces,

00:00:18.264 --> 00:00:22.727
but somehow managed to get me through
one of the world's toughest Ironmen.

00:00:23.519 --> 00:00:26.981
And also, more recently,

00:00:26.981 --> 00:00:28.316
a half-marathon.

00:00:28.691 --> 00:00:34.113
Now, I did these to show
what living with HIV is like now,